I"ö<h3 id="flexible">Flexible</h3>

<p>Complete freedom to use whichever templating language, build tool and organisational model best suits your project.</p>

<h3 id="integrated">Integrated</h3>

<p>Seamlessly integrate your component library into your site, app or build tools by including it as a dependency in your build.</p>

<h3 id="data-driven">Data-driven</h3>

<p>Component preview data can be hardcoded or dynamically generated any way you like - for instance using libraries such as Faker.</p>
